.000Z","msg":"唉... 還好吧"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:13:26.000Z","msg":"被人打咗 幾多支針呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家好返晒未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:16:05.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻⋯⋯嘻⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n唔⋯⋯知⋯⋯呢⋯⋯嘻嘻⋯⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:17:08.000Z","msg":"睇嚟好返晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以出院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}